---
title: Chipotle Pork, Corn and Pepper Bowl with Zesty Couscous and Cheese
description: This delicious Chipotle Pork, Corn and Pepper Bowl has been expertly designed by our chefs as a lighter option to help with a balanced lifestyle.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF230125_R26_W10_UK_L13288-3_Main_low-f117cdc1.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/chipotle-pork-corn-and-pepper-bowl-63b56f0db1ab4b4b8a219528-f55de112.pdf
